Package: apsfs
Title: Monte Carlo code for simulation of atmospheric Point Spread Functions and spatially-resolved Spherical Albedo Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Alexandre", "Castagna", email = "alexandre.castagna@eoplus.science", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package implementing backward Monte Carlo radiative transfer to calculate the atmospheric Point Spread Function and the spatially-resolved Spherical Albedo Function.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
